0on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20invitation%20of%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia...%20the%20Organisation's%20Executive%20Committee%20is%20convening%20an%20urgent%20open-ended%20extraordinary%20meeting%20at%20the%20ministerial%20level%2C%20to%20address%20the%20escalating%20military%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20and%20its%20environs%20as%20well%20as%20the%20deteriorating%20conditions%20that%20endanger%20the%20lives%20of%20civilians%20and%20the%20overall%20security%20and%20stability%20of%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20OIC%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20OIC%20is%20the%20second-largest%20organisation%20after%20the%20United%20Nations%20with%20a%20membership%20of%2057%20nations%20spread%20over%20four%20continents.%20It%20calls%20itself%20%26quot%3Bthe%20collective%20voice%20of%20the%20Muslim%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20OIC's%20urgent%20meeting%20call%20comes%20on%20a%20day%20Saudi%20Arabia%20suspended%20talks%20on%20potentially%20normalising%20ties%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20launched%20a%20large-scale%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20which%20killed%201%2C300%20people%2C%20sparking%20a%20retaliatory%20bombing%20campaign%20that%20has%20killed%20at%20least%202%2C215%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20ahead%20of%20a%20potential%20Israeli%20ground%20invasion%20of%20the%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSaudi%20Arabia%20has%20decided%20to%20pause%20discussion%20on%20possible%20normalisation%20and%20has%20informed%20US%20officials%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20familiar%20with%20the%20discussions%20told%20news%20agency%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Gulf%20kingdom%2C%20home%20to%20the%20holiest%20sites%20in%20Islam%2C%20has%20never%20recognised%20Israel%20and%20did%20not%20join%20the%202020%20US-brokered%20Abraham%20Accords%20that%20saw%20its%20Gulf%20neighbours%20Bahrain%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20as%20well%20as%20Morocco%20establish%20formal%20ties%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20had%20been%20pushing%20hard%20in%20recent%20months%20for%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20take%20the%20same%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20de%20facto%20ruler%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%2C%20son%20of%20the%20ageing%20King%20Salman%2C%20Riyadh%20had%20laid%20out%20conditions%20for%20normalisation%20including%20security%20guarantees%20from%20Washington%20and%20help%20developing%20a%20civilian%20nuclear%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20week%20since%20Hamas%20launched%20its%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20Riyadh%20has%20voiced%20increasing%20disquiet%20about%20the%20fate%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20Hamas-controlled%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20where%20Israel%20has%20launched%20thousands%20of%20strikes%20and%20ordered%20the%20evacuation%20of%20the%20territory's%20north%2C%20prompting%20thousands%20to%20flee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20denounced%20the%20displacement%20of%20Palestinians%20within%20Gaza%20and%20attacks%20on%20%26quot%3Bdefenceless%20civilians%26quot%3B%2C%20its%20strongest%20language%20criticising%20Israel%20since%20the%20war%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20AFP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697286240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F784tv3ig_khan-yunis-gaza-afp_625x300_14_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fislamic-nations-group-calls-urgent-extraordinary-meet-on-israel-gaza-4481200%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20top%20grouping%20of%20Islamic%20nations%20has%20called%20an%20%26quot%3Burgent%20extraordinary%20meeting%26quot%3B%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20discuss%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fislamic-nations-group-calls-urgent-extraordinary-meet-on-israel-gaza-4481200%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%