fied%20soon%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20will%20face%20significant%20challenges%20caused%20by%20political%20and%20institutional%20contestations%20of%20intergovernmental%20fiscal%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%2C%20he%20writes%2C%20make%20business%20untenable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20reports%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fpolicy%2Findian-govt-to-set-16th-finance-commission-soon-chairman-and-members-to-be-selected-next%2Farticleshow%2F103759824.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eworking%20to%20set%20up%20the%2016th%20Finance%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20commission%20is%20tasked%20with%20fine-tuning%20how%20resources%20are%20shared%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20states.%20This%20finance%20commission%E2%80%99s%20term%2C%20however%2C%20is%20till%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERoy%20notes%20how%20the%2014th%20Finance%20Commission%20report%20abolished%20grants%20and%20increased%20devolution%20of%20funds%20to%20states%2C%20which%20was%20then%20followed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20promote%20cooperative%20federalism.%20%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20this%20has%20reversed%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted%2C%20highlighting%20how%20the%20abolition%20of%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20has%20given%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%20supreme%20discretionary%20powers%20over%20capital%20grants.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20authoritarian%2C%20Roy%20notes%20that%20this%20government%20signifies%20a%20weak%20sort%20of%20authoritarianism%2C%20citing%20the%20transfer%20of%20government%20audit%20officials%20who%20pointed%20out%20problems%20with%20flagship%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20of%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20Roy%20calls%20an%20%E2%80%9Cembarrassment.%E2%80%9D%20He%20wrote%20that%20it%20lacked%20understanding%20and%20tried%20to%20corner%20central%20spending%20on%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%2016th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20he%20notes%2C%20the%20states%20are%20higher%20as%20central%20fiscal%20deficit%20is%20at%20a%20record%20high%2C%20tax%20revenue%20increase%20efforts%20have%20failed%20and%20total%20public%20sector%20capital%20expenditure%20has%20not%20increased.%20Roy%20points%20to%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20been%20depriving%20states%20of%20their%20rightful%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20piece%2C%20Roy%20also%20calls%20for%20prudent%20allocation%20of%20tax%20revenues%20among%20states%20and%20a%20fresh%20look%20at%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20to%20make%20it%20more%20workable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Roy%20calls%20on%20the%20government%20to%20constitute%20the%2016th%20Finance%20Commission%20%E2%80%9Csensitively.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697286034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14174913%2FScreenshot-2023-10-14-at-5.48.05%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fwhy-the-16th-finance-commissions-struggles-will-be-significant%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20Business%20Standard%20opinion%20piece%2C%20Rathin%20Roy%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Overseas%20Development%20Institute%20in%20London%2C%20has%20highlighted%20the%20role%20of%20political%20and%20institutional%20contestations%20on%20intergovernmental%20fiscal%20relations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fwhy-the-16th-finance-commissions-struggles-will-be-significant%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%20Launches%20Probe%20into%20Adani%20Group's%20Two%20Airports%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14173625%2F1200px-Mumbai_International_Airport.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20on%20Friday%2C%20October%2013%2C%20informed%20stock%20exchanges%20that%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%20is%20carrying%20out%20a%20probe%20into%20its%20two%20Mumbai%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20said%20probe%20authorities%20sought%20information%20relating%20to%20finances%20and%20other%20documents%20of%20Mumbai%20International%20Airport%20Ltd%20(MIAL)%20and%20Navi%20Mumbai%20International%20Airport%20Ltd%20(NMIAL)%20for%20the%20period%20between%20financial%20years%202017-18%20and%202021-22.%20The%20acquisition%20of%20the%20airports%20by%20the%20group%20was%20completed%20in%20the%202021-22%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMIAL%20and%20NMIAL%20have%20received%20communications%20from%20the%20said%20Authority%20about%20the%20initiation%20of%20investigations%20of%20books%20of%20accounts%20and%20other%20books%20and%20papers%20in%20terms%20section%20210(1)%20of%20the%20Companies%20Act%2C%202013%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adani%20Enterprises%20said%20on%20BSE%20filing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fministry-probing-accounts-of-adani-enterprises-two-airports-mumbai-and-navi-mumbai-airport-11697244889820.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveMint%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202021%2C%20the%20group%20acquired%20a%2074%25%20stake%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20international%20airport%2C%20after%20buying%20GVK%20Group%E2%80%99s%2050.5%25%20stake%20and%20a%2023.5%25%20stake%20from%20ACSA%20Global%20Ltd%20and%20Bid%20Services%20Division%20(Mauritius)%20Ltd%20(Bidvest).%20It%20also%20secured%20rights%20to%20build%20and%20operate%20the%20Navi%20Mumbai%20airport%2C%20where%20operations%20will%20commence%20from%20December%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20country%2C%20the%20group%20owns%20and%20operates%20seven%20airports.%20It%20won%20bids%20for%20six%20airports%20under%20the%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%20(AAI)%20in%20February%202019%2C%20including%20Lucknow%2C%20Mangaluru%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Guwahati%2C%20and%20Thiruvananthapuram.%20The%20group%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20operating%2C%20managing%2C%20and%20developing%20airports%20for%20over%2050%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20underway%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20troubles%20the%20conglomerate%20has%20been%20through%20since%20a%20US%20short%20seller%20earlier%20this%20year%20accused%20it%20of%20improperly%20using%20offshore%20tax%20havens%20and%20stock%20manipulation.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20group%20said%2C%20it%20will%20respond%20to%20communication%20received%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%20in%20%E2%80%9Caccordance%20with%20applicable%20legal%20provisions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20different%20probe%20into%20suspected%20violations%20in%20overseas%20investments%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group%20by%20the%20Securities%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20regulator%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdrawn%20a%20blank%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20court-appointed%20panel%20said%20in%20May%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-enterprises-says-ministry-to-initiate-probe-into-two-units-books-2726007%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697285594000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14173625%2F1200px-Mumbai_International_Airport.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fministry-of-corporate-affairs-launches-probe-into-adani-groups-two-airports-in-mumbai%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20conglomerate%20said%20probe%20authorities%20sought%20information%20relating%20to%20finances%20and%20other%20documents%20of%20Mumbai%20International%20Airport%20Ltd%20and%20Navi%20Mumbai%20International%20Airport%20Ltd%20from%202017-18%20to%202021-22.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%2