C%22%20height%3D%5C%222439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIain%20and%20Brioni%20Cameron%20say%20they'll%20continue%20living%20on%20their%20boat%20until%20a%20more%20exciting%20adventure%20comes%20along.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Iain%20Cameron%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIain%20Cameron%20and%20his%20wife%20Brioni%20left%20Scotland%20and%20moved%20onto%20a%20boat%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20in%202020.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESince%20they%20moved%20onto%20the%20boat%2C%20he%20says%20they've%20only%20spent%20three%20nights%20sleeping%20on%20land.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECameron%20says%20they've%20faced%20storms%2C%20huge%20waves%2C%20and%20failing%20engines%2C%20but%20he%20wouldn't%20change%20a%20thing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Iain%20Cameron%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fredseas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EYouTuber%20and%20adventurer%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20from%20Glasgow%2C%20Scotland.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-on-a-boat-housing-affordability-travel-around-the-world-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20on%20a%20boat%20came%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20me%20one%20day%2C%20in%202016%2C%20when%20I%20stumbled%20across%20a%20video%20of%20sailboats%20in%20the%20tropics.%20When%20I%20started%20working%20remotely%2C%20I%20figured%20I%20could%20do%20my%20job%20from%20a%20boat%20rather%20than%20my%20sofa%20in%20rainy%20Glasgow%2C%20Scotland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20I%20presented%20my%20wife%20Brioni%20with%20the%20idea%20to%20sell%20everything%20we%20owned%20to%20move%20onto%20a%20boat%2C%20her%20first%20response%20was%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20hate%20boats.%26quot%3B%20Besides%2C%20we%20both%20had%20stable%20jobs%20in%20Scotland%3A%20Brioni%20was%20an%20elementary%20school%20teacher%20and%20I%20worked%20in%20tech%20as%20an%20international%20technical%20trainer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20we%20came%20up%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20test%20the%20idea%20and%20it%20worked%20out.%20For%20over%20two%20years%20now%2C%20living%20on%20a%20boat%20has%20made%20us%20stronger%2C%20more%20confident%2C%20and%20more%20appreciative.%20I%20think%20we've%20traveled%20through%20almost%2025%20countries%20and%20sailed%20over%2012%2C000%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20tested%20the%20idea%20three%20times%20before%20moving%20onto%20our%20own%20boat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20we%20tested%20the%20idea%20by%20sailing%20on%20my%20dad's%20boat%20near%20our%20home.%20Our%20first%20experience%20was%20wet%20and%20cold%2C%20but%20later%20we%20sailed%20a%20catamaran%20near%20Edinburgh%2C%20Scotland.%20It%20went%20much%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20later%2C%20we%20chartered%20a%20catamaran%20out%20of%20Dubrovnik%2C%20Croatia%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20spending%20two%20weeks%20in%20the%20Adriatic%20Sea.%20On%20our%20return%2C%20we%20were%20still%20talking%20to%20each%20other%20and%20we%20still%20wanted%20to%20be%20on%20the%20boat%20together.%20A%20month%20passed%20and%20we%20moved%20to%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20selling%20everything%20we%20had%20to%20raise%20funds%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-boat-loans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20our%20own%20boat%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sold%20most%20of%20our%20things%20through%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20and%20eBay.%20The%20remaining%20stuff%20was%20sold%20to%20friends%20and%20family.%20The%20only%20items%20we%20didn't%20sell%20were%20two%20guitars%20that%20we%20loved%20too%20much%20to%20part%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20flew%20to%20Saint%20Vincent%20and%20the%20Grenadines%20to%20buy%20our%20boat%2C%20but%20we%20felt%20scammed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20talking%20with%20a%20guy%20on%20Facebook%20Messenger%20who%20said%20he%20had%20a%20boat%20for%20sale%20in%20Saint%20Vincent%20and%20the%20Grenadines.%20The%20United%20Kingdom%20shut%20down%20for%20the%20pandemic%2C%20but%20when%20the%20lockdown%20lifted%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20we%20put%20our%20apartment%20on%20the%20market%2C%20bought%20one-way%20tickets%20to%20the%20islands%2C%20and%20left%20with%20only%20our%20backpacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223252%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brioni%20and%20Iain%20Cameron%20on%20the%20beach.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529c92e55f52b01b35fb75b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrioni%20and%20Iain%20taking%20a%20beach%20selfie.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Iain%20Cameron%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20arrived%2C%20we%20found%20out%20it%20was%20something%20of%20a%20scam.%20The%20boat%20was%20trashed.%20We%20repaired%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20at%20our%20expense%20before%20the%20original%20owner%20told%20us%20the%20deal%20was%20off%20and%20we%20had%20to%20get%20off%20the%20boat.%20He%20released%20our%20deposit%20and%20we%20effectively%20became%20homeless%20for%20a%20few%20months%2C%20backpacking%20our%20way%20up%20through%20the%20Caribbean%20in%20search%20of%20a%20different%20boat%20to%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20we%20boat%20sat%20for%20a%20couple%20we%20had%20met%20in%20the%20boat%20yard%20and%20even%20lived%20in%20a%20shipping%20container.%20We%20eventually%20found%20a%20boat%20to%20buy%20through%20YachtWorld%2C%20which%20is%20like%20the%20auto%20trader%20of%20boats%20around%20the%20world%2C%20in%20December%202020.%20Our%20boat%20is%20a%20Leopard%2047%20built%20by%20Robertson%20%26amp%3B%20Caine%20in%202005.%20It's%20a%20catamaran%20with%204%20queen%20size%20beds%20each%20with%20en%20suite%2C%20a%20galley%20or%20a%20small%20kitchen%2C%20a%20saloon%2C%20and%20a%20cockpit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223252%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iain%20and%20Briodi%20Cameron%20posing%20on%20their%20boat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529c7fb68f1d46f52b1d2df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222008%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIain%20and%20Brioni%20sailing%20on%20their%20boat%20in%20the%20Caribbean.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Iain%20Cameron%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20wreck%20and%20needed%20huge%20amounts%20of%20work.%20We%20did%20%E2%80%94%20and%20do%20%E2%80%94%20all%20our%20boat%20work%20ourselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELife%20on%20the%20water%20is%20more%20taxing%20than%20it%20sounds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20on%20a%20boat%20wants%20to%20break%2C%20given%20the%20harsh%20salty%20environment.%20A%20simple%20mistake%20can%20result%20in%20sinking.%20Moreover%2C%20traveling%20from%20point%20A%20to%20B%20takes%20planning.%20A%20passage%20usually%20lasts%20a%20few%20days%20and%20when%20you're%20tired%20you%20can't%20just%20drop%20the%20anchor%20for%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20think%20life%20on%20the%20water%20is%20just%20sunshine%20and%20bikinis%2C%20but%20it%20also%20includes%20fixing%20plumbing%20and%20getting%20in%20the%20water%20to%20clean%20the%20barnacles%20off%20your%20hull.%20Our%20most%20recent%20challenges%20have%20been%20passage%20related.%20We%20recently%20crossed%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%2C%20which%20took%20us%2040%20days.%20Each%20day%2C%20we%20alternated%20spending%20eight%20hours%20on%20watch%20and%20eight%20hours%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223252%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iain%20and%20Brioni%20Cameron's%20boat%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20ocean.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529c85068f1d46f52b1d2ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221808%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIain%20says%20living%20full%20time%20on%20a%20boat%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20maintenance.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Iain%20Cameron%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20time%2C%20we%20faced%20lightning%20storms%2C%20huge%20waves%2C%20failing%20engines%2C%20no%20wind%2C%20too%20much%20wind%2C%20a%20broken%20oven%2C%20and%20ripped%20sails.%20Our%20food%20supply%20was%20destroyed%20by%20weevils%20and%20we%20had%20our%20steering%20system%20fail%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20which%20almost%20resulted%20in%20us%20having%20to%20abandon%20ship%20thousands%20of%20miles%20from%20another%20living%20soul.%20But%20we%20wouldn't%20change%20anything%20for%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cruising%20community%20is%20incredible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20been%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20form%20amazing%20friendships%20across%20the%20globe.%20We%20usually%20use%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20keep%20doing%20it%20unless%20a%20more%20exciting%20adventure%20comes%20along%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20living%20on%20a%20boat%20is%20an%20exciting%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20the%20quiet%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20monthly%20energy%20costs%20are%20quite%20small%20at%20around%20%2450%2C%20and%20our%20carbon%20footprint%20has%20almost%20vanished%2C%20as%20we%20travel%20using%20the%20power%20of%20the%20wind%2099%25%20of%20the%20time.%20Very%20rarely%20do%20we%20actually%20use%20our%20engines.%20We%20generate%20100%25%20of%20our%20electrical%20power%20from%20solar%20panels%20on%20the%20roof.%20We%20catch%20most%20of%20our%20food%20fishing%20with%20a%20hand%20reel%20or%20spear%2C%20and%20we%20find%20our%20fruit%20and%20vegetables%20from%20local%20markets%20when%20we%20dock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20almost%20three%20years%2C%20we've%20spent%20a%20total%20of%20three%20nights%20on%20land%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnchoring%20at%20a%20dock%20is%20free%2C%20pretty%20much%20everywhere%20we've%20been%2C%20but%20we've%20had%20to%20pay%20marine%20reserve%20fees%20in%20some%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbonaire-caribbean-island-surprising-things-world-traveler-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20places%20like%20Bonaire%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpanama-island-locals-relocated-climate-change-photos-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGuna%20Yala%2C%20Panama%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20usually%20cost%20around%20%2410%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20monthly%20expenses%20are%20in%20the%20region%20of%20%241%2C400.%20That%20covers%20food%2C%20fuel%2C%20Starlink%20internet%2C%20and%20most%20repair%20parts%20we%20need.%20Months%20fluctuate%20a%20lot%2C%20so%20it's%20hard%20to%20land%20an%20exact%20number.%20When%20we%20spent%2040%20days%20sailing%20across%20the%20Pacific%2C%20we%20didn't%20spend%20any%20money.%20But%20when%20we%20anchored%20we%20had%20to%20buy%20lots%20of%20food%20and%20parts%20for%20everything%20that%20broke%20so%20our%20bill%20was%20much%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20started%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20and%20Patreon%20to%20document%20our%20adventures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20enjoy%20the%20process%20of%20filming%20and%20editing%20our%20weekly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fredseas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EYouTube%20episodes%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20our%20big%20challenge%20is%20growing%20our%20audience.%20To%20help%20us%20reach%20more%20people%2C%20we%20launched%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.red-seas.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20Red%20Seas%20website%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20are%20currently%20on%20a%20mini%20world%20tour.%20We%20also%20host%20and%20maintain%20websites%20for%20people%2C%20and%20work%20with%20a%20boat%20navigation%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223252%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20ocean.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529c8f455f52b01b35fb73d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20view%20of%20Iain%20and%20Brioni%20sailing%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20an%20island.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Iain%20Cameron%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20been%20invited%20to%20speak%20at%20many%20boating%20events%20and%20clubs%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20the%20Southampton%20International%20Boat%20Show%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20Annapolis%20Boat%20Show%20in%20the%20US.%20We%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-money-patreon-subscribers-creators-earn-income-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eset%20up%20some%20Patreon%3C%2Fa%3E%20meet-ups%20to%20thank%20those%20who%20support%20us%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20all%20that%20Red%20Seas%20does%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20inspire%20everyone%20to%20take%20the%20leap%20and%20find%20their%20own%20adventure.%20That%20may%20be%20sailing%2C%20van%20life%2C%20parenthood%2C%20or%20who%20knows%20what%20else.%20If%20we%20can%20be%20an%20example%20of%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20go%20both%20feet%20in%2C%20perhaps%20others%20won't%20be%20so%20afraid.%20The%20adventure%20is%20usually%20far%20better%20than%20you%20could've%20imagined%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20live%20on%20a%20boat%20full%20time%20or%20have%20an%20adventurous%20living%20situation%20and%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20email%20Manseen%20Logan%20at%20mlogan%40insider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsold-everything-to-live-on-a-boat-full-time-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697284741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652973fd6561dd877e7a381d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsold-everythin