indicated%20that%20Hamas%20intended%20to%20kill%20or%20hold%20civilians%20as%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20page%20titled%20%26quot%3BTop%20Secret%26quot%3B%20included%20details%20of%20the%20plan%20for%20an%20attack%20on%20Kfar%20Sa'ad%20asking%20%26quot%3BCombat%20unit%201%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontain%20the%20new%20Da'at%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20%26quot%3BCombat%20unit%202%26quot%3B%20was%20directed%20to%20%26quot%3Bcollect%20hostages%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bsearch%20the%20Bnei%20Akiva%20youth%20centre%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsearch%20the%20old%20Da'at%20school%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20page%20labelled%20%26quot%3BTop%20Secret%20Maneuver%26quot%3B%20outlined%20a%20plan%20for%20a%20Hamas%20unit%20to%20secure%20the%20Kfar%20Sa'ad's%20east%20side%20while%20a%20second%20unit%20controls%20the%20west.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20plan%2C%20Hamas%20units%20were%20directed%20to%20%26quot%3Bkill%20as%20many%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcapture%20hostages%26quot%3B.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20Hamas%20units%20were%20asked%20to%20surround%20a%20dining%20hall%20and%20hold%20hostages%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20to%20attack%20Kfar%20Sa'ad%20is%20part%20of%20documents%20that%20are%20being%20analysed%20by%20Israeli%20officials%2C%20NBC%20reported%20citing%20a%20source%20in%20the%20Israeli%20army%20and%20one%20in%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Israeli%20officials%2C%20the%20documents%20revealed%20that%20Hamas%20had%20been%20systematically%20gathering%20intelligence%20on%20each%20kibbutz%20which%20shares%20borders%20with%20Gaza%20and%20creating%20specific%20plans%20of%20attack%20for%20each%20village%20that%20included%20the%20intentional%20targeting%20of%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20source%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20dental%20office%2C%20the%20supermarket%2C%20the%20dining%20hall%2C%26quot%3B%20NBC%20News%20reported.%20T