023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20grandfather%20fought%20his%20way%20through%20a%20land%20of%20death%20and%20chaos%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20The%20Atlantic%2C%20Amir%20described%20in%20detail%20how%20his%20father%20rescued%20him%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%2C%20his%20wife%20Miri%2C%20and%20their%20two%20daughters%20were%20asleep%20at%20their%20kibbutz%20when%20they%20heard%20the%20sound%20of%20a%20mortar%20about%20to%20explode%20at%20about%206%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20ran%20to%20their%20safe%20room%2C%20built%20to%20withstand%20direct%20hits%20from%20mortars%20or%20rockets%2C%20where%20they%20put%20their%20daughters%2C%20three-year-old%20Galia%2C%20and%20one-year-old%20Carmel%2C%20to%20bed%20every%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20Amir%20described%20the%20gunfire%20they%20heard%20from%20the%20fields%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20chilling%20noise%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20heard%20in%20his%20lifetime.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20realized%20Hamas%20militants%20had%20infiltrated%20their%20kibbutz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tibons%20and%20their%20daughters%20waited%20together%20in%20silence%20and%20in%20darkness%2C%20unsure%20if%20anyone%20was%20coming%20to%20rescue%20them.%20Amir%20texted%20his%20parents%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20terrorists%20outside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20parents%20started%20driving%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%20and%20arrived%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Sderot%20to%20find%20people%20walking%20barefoot%20on%20the%20road.%20They%20were%20young%20people%20who%20had%20fled%20the%20music%20festival%20that%20Hamas%20fighters%20had%20attacked%20early%20that%20morning%2C%20massacring%C2%A0%20260%20people.%20%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20put%20the%20survivors%20in%20their%20car%20and%20took%20them%20farther%20away%20from%20the%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20Amir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20then%20plowed%20on%20through%20the%20war%20zone%2C%20picking%20up%20a%20soldier%20along%20the%20way.%20Soon%2C%20they%20ran%20into%20a%20gunbattle%20between%20Israeli%20forces%20and%20a%20%26quot%3BHamas%20cell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20has%20a%20pistol%20with%20him%2C%20and%20he%20and%20this%20other%20soldier%20join%20the%20soldiers%20who%20are%20fighting.%20They%20help%20kill%20them%2C%20and%20now%20they're%20very%20close%20to%20my%20kibbutz%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Amir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20battle%20has%20left%20two%20soldiers%20wounded.%20Noam%20puts%20them%20in%20his%20car%2C%20and%20Amir's%20mother%20then%20took%20the%20wounded%20soldiers%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20took%20weapons%20from%20the%20wounded%20soldiers%2C%20who%20gave%20them%20to%20him%20because%20he%20told%20them%2C%20'I'm%20going%20back%20in%2C'%26quot%3B%20Amir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20amid%20the%20chaos%2C%20Amir%20said%20his%20father%20ran%20into%20another%20retired%20former%20general%2C%20Israel%20Ziv%2C%20who%20had%20donned%20his%20uniform%20and%20immediately%20headed%20to%20join%20the%20fighting%20when%20the%20Hamas%20invasion%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20two%20guys%20over%20the%20age%20of%2060%20are%20driving%20in%20a%20regular%20car%20like%20people%20take%20on%20the%20New%20Jersey%20Turnpike%20on%20their%20way%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Amir%20told%20The%20Atlantic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Nahal%20Oz%2C%20the%20Tibon%20family%2C%20sitting%20in%20the%20darkness%20of%20their%20safe%20room%2C%20could%20hear%20a%20battle%20that%20had%20begun%20outside.%20%26quot%3BMy%20father%20is%20coming.%20They're%20fighting.%20He's%20with%20these%20soldiers%2C%26quot%3B%20Amir%20told%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoam%20had%20joined%20up%20with%20a%20cohort%20of%20Israeli%20soldiers%20sent%20to%20liberate%20the%20kibbutz.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20came%20to%20the%20area%20of%20my%20son's%20house%20there%20was%20at%20least%20five%20bodies%20of%20terrorists%20and%20a%20brave%20Israeli%20soldier.%20When%20I%20came%20to%20their%20apartment%20I%20knock%20on%20the%20security%20window%20and%20I%20say%20'Amir.%20It's%20father%2C%20you%20can%20open.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20that%201%2C300%20people%20were%20killed%20during%20Hamas'%20deadly%20raids%2C%20terrorist%20attacks%20and%20rocket%20barrages%20that%20began%20on%20October%207.%20The%20Palestinian%20death%20toll%20as%20a%20result%20of%20retaliatory%20bombing%20by%20Israel%20of%20Gaza%20is%20at%20least%201%2C900%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Flivecoverage%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-strip%2Fcard%2Flatest-death-toll-in-israel-and-gaza-eoVPFI8WcXN0mzIR73pY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-general-rescued-family-from-hamas-like-liam-neeson-taken-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697281977000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652a75c955f52b01b35fbe28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-general-rescued-family-from-hamas-like-liam-neeson-taken-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Israeli%20grandfather%20and%20retired%20IDF%20general%20who%20rescued%20his%20granddaughters%20from%20Hamas%20is%20being%20compared%20on%20social%20media%20to%20Liam%20Neeson%20in%20%26quot%3BTaken.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-general-rescued-family-from-hamas-like-liam-neeson-taken-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kohli%20meets%20his%20idol%20Tendulkar%20ahead%20of%20India-Pakistan%20clash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697281820000%2C%