rrant%20against%20Pramot%20Singh%2C%20chief%20of%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20group%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehillsjournal.com%2Fcourt-orders-non-bailable-arrest-warrant-to-meitei-leepun-chief-pramot-directs-churachandpur-sp-for-timely-execution-of-order%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hills%20Journal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKuki%20groups%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20group%20%E2%80%93%20like%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20%E2%80%93%20is%20instigating%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20but%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20have%20denied%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20order%20also%20directed%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20to%20ensure%20the%20timely%20execution%20of%20the%20order%20which%20is%20returnable%20by%20November%209%2C%202023%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETHJ%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETHJ%20reported%20that%20at%20the%20court%20hearing%2C%20the%20assistant%20public%20prosecutor%20submitted%20that%20during%20the%20course%20of%20investigation%2C%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20address%20was%20established%20as%20Nepali%20Basti%20Chingmeirong%2C%20Imphal%20West%20District%2C%20Manipur%2C%20which%20lies%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20Lamphel%20Police%20Station%2C%20Imphal%20West%2C%20and%20its%20office%20is%20at%20Sana%20Konung%2C%20Imphal%20East%20District%2C%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Investigating%20Officer%20of%20the%20case%20stated%20that%20Singh%20could%20not%20be%20arrested%20now%20as%20his%20address%20now%20falls%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20Lamphel%20Police%20Station%2C%20Imphal%20West%20District.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20a%20message%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Officer-in-Charge%20of%20the%20Station%20to%20take%20necessary%20action%2C%20including%20conducting%20a%20house%20search%20on%20September%209%20under%20Section%2041A%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%20there%20was%20no%20response%2C%20despite%20a%20reminder%20also%20being%20sent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20was%20also%20served%20a%20notice%20to%20appear%20in%20person%20before%20the%20investigating%20officer%20on%20October%202%2C%202023%20at%2010%3A00%20am%20at%20Churachandpur%20Police%20Station%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20cooperate%20or%20give%20a%20reply%2C%20THJ%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Court%20hence%20issued%20a%20non-bailable%20arrest%20warrant%20against%20Singh.%20It%20also%20directed%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20to%20ensure%20timely%20execution%20of%20the%20order%20which%20is%20returnable%20by%20November%209%2C%202023%2C%20per%20THJ.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%208%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-meitei-leepun-pramot-singh-case-enmity%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eregistered%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20by%20the%20Kuki%20Students%20Organisation%20against%20Singh%2C%20regarding%20both%20tweets%20he%20and%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20posted%20online%2C%20as%20well%20as%20comments%20he%20made%20in%20an%20interview%20he%20gave%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20June%206%20this%20year.%20In%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20says%20that%20all%20Kukis%20would%20be%20wiped%20out%20or%20annihilated%20from%20Manipur.%20The%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20had%20reacted%20strongly%20against%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FIR%20against%20Singh%20invokes%20charges%20including%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups%2C%20intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20peace%