s%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Findia-vs-pakistan-world-cup-2023-make-my-trips-newspaper-ad-for-pakistani-fans-divides-internet-4480930%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Senior%20Journalist%20KS%20Sachidananda%20Murthy%20Passes%20Away%20at%2068%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14155040%2FF8X29BkbEAAeSx6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESenior%20journalist%20K.S.%20Sachidananda%20Murthy%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20resident%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EMalayala%20Manorama%3C%2Fem%3E%20daily%20in%20Delhi%2C%20passed%20away%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Friday%2C%20October%2013.%20He%20was%2068.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Sachi%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20he%20was%20widely%20known%20in%20journalist%20circles%2C%20had%20a%20four-decade-long%20career%20in%20journalism%20and%20most%20of%20which%20was%20spent%20in%20Malayala%20Manorama%20Group%20and%20in%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fi%3E%20magazine.%20Before%20that%2C%20he%20had%20a%20stint%20with%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20served%20as%20the%20secretary%20general%20of%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20and%20chairman%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Press%20Advisory%20Committee.%20He%20also%20held%20a%20stint%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Central%20Press%20Accreditation%20Committee%20and%20the%20Press%20Council%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMalayala%20Manorama%3C%2Fem%3E%20ran%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%20popular%20political%20column%20%3Cem%3EDesheeyam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(originally%20called%20New%20Delhi)%20on%20its%20edit%20pages%20for%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20native%20of%20Kolar%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Murthy%20was%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Media%20Academy%20Award%20for%20lifetime%20contribution%20to%20journalism.%20He%20has%20covered%20multiple%20overseas%20visits%20of%20presidents%20and%20prime%20ministers.%20%E2%80%9CSachidananda%20Murthy%20was%20among%20the%20few%20Kannadiga%20journalists%20active%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20media%20circles%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20breathed%20his%20last%2C%20Murthy%20was%20recovering%20from%20a%20recent%20lung%20transplant%20surgery%20in%20the%20city.%20He%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20sons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Findia-and-maldives-ties-despite-china-bound-by-history-and-geography-8981993%2F%5C%22%3EWriting%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20journalist%20Debashish%20Mukerji%20traces%20Murthy%E2%80%99s%20professional%20trajectory%20from%20being%20a%20correspondent%20in%20Bangalore%20to%20a%20widely%20known%20and%20highly%20regarded%20journalist%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20he%20knew%20everyone%20who%20mattered%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20across%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20diplomatic%20circles.%20Correspondents%20of%20regional%20publications%20in%20Delhi%20often%20restrict%20themselves%20largely%20to%20politicians%20from%20their%20own%20state%2C%20who%20know%20their%20publications%E2%80%99%20worth%2C%20finding%20access%20challenging%20to%20those%20from%20other%20regions%2C%20who%20often%20may%20not%20have%20heard%20of%20the%20publications%20they%20represent.%20But%20Sachi%E2%80%99s%20network%20went%20way%20beyond%20Kerala%20politicians%20(or%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20those%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20his%20home%20state)%2C%20embracing%20key%20players%20across%20the%20aisle%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20Mukherji%2C%20who%20worked%20under%20Murthy%20whilst%20he%20was%20at%20%3Cem%3EMalayala%20Manorama.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20remembers%20Murthy%20as%20someone%20who%20rarely%20made%20political%20predictions%2C%20but%20whenever%20he%20did%2C%20he%20got%20them%20right.%20%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20stress%20that%20describing%20Sachi%20as%20a%20purely%20political%20animal%20would%20be%20doing%20him%20a%20disservice.%20I%20was%20often%20struck%20by%20the%20sheer%20range%20of%20his%20other%20interests%2C%20though%20he%20rarely%20wrote%20about%20them%2C%20which%20included%20movies%2C%20food%2C%20travel%2C%20mythology%20and%20music%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20Mukherji.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEGI%20deeply%20condoles%20the%20passing%20away%20of%20senior%20journalist%20and%20former%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Guild%2C%20Mr.%20Sachidananda%20Murthy%20(Sachi).%20He%20was%20a%20pillar%20of%20strength%20for%20the%20Guild%20and%20an%20inspiration%20for%20all%20journalists.%20Sachi%20will%20be%20dearly%20missed%20by%20all%20his%20colleagues%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20remembered%20him%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20shaped%20generations%20of%20reporters%20%26amp%3B%20his%20guidance%20was%20readily%20available%20to%20all.%20His%20charming%20ways%20easily%20won%20everyone.%20We%20all%20will%20miss%20him%20sorely.%20PCI%20pays%20its%20humble%20tributes%20to%20him%20and%20prays%20for%20eternal%20peace%20to%20his%20departed%20soul.%20Thank%20You%20Sachi%20for%20being%20part%20of%20our%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697279279000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14155040%2FF8X29BkbEAAeSx6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fsenior-journalist-ks-sachidananda-murthy-passes-away-at-68%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Sachi'%2C%20as%20he%20was%20widely%20known%20in%20journalist%20circles%2C%20had%20a%20four-decade-long%20career%20in%20journalism%20and%20most%20of%20which%20was%20spent%20in%20the%20Malayala%20Manorama%20Group%20and%20in%C2%A0The%20Week%20magazine.%20Before%20that%2C%20he%20had%20a%20stint%20with%20the%20Ind