%20GPS%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20military%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it's%20the%20rapidly%20innovating%20Ukrainians%20or%20the%20well-resourced%20Americans%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20able%20to%20totally%20defend%20its%20troops%20against%20drones%20at%20all%20times.%20Technologies%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fland%2F2023%2F08%2F11%2Fus-army-working-through-challenges-with-laser-weapons%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elasers%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20help%20someday%2C%20but%20not%20in%20time%20for%20an%20Israeli%20assault%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israel%20soldiers%20drone%20Gaza%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652982f668f1d46f52b16a22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESoldiers%20in%20southern%20Israel%20prepare%20to%20launch%20a%20reconnaissance%20drone%20near%20the%20border%20with%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20in%20August%202020.%3Cp%3EJACK%20GUEZ%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20counter-UAV%20skills%20may%20also%20not%20be%20evenly%20distributed%20among%20its%20troops.%20The%20IDF%20does%20have%20counter-drone%20capabilities%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20they%20are%20generally%20held%20at%20quite%20high%20echelon%2C%20and%20that's%20partly%20a%20result%20of%20them%20having%20a%20mostly%20conscript%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20Watling%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20level%20of%20training%20in%20the%20IDF%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20breadth%20of%20skill%20set%20that%20each%20soldier%20has%20is%20actually%20quite%20limited%20because%20they%20tend%20to%20keep%20people%20as%20reserves%26quot%3B%20and%20train%20them%20for%20specific%20tasks%2C%20Watling%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20that%20leads%20to%20is%20that%20you%20end%20up%20with%20kernels%20of%20excellence%20but%20the%20level%20of%20integration%20is%20actually%20less%20than