ns%20that%20say%20%26quot%3Bon%20strike%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunion%20baristas%20stand%20with%20WGA%20%26amp%3B%20SAG-AFTRA!%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529817e55f52b01b35f4463%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStarbucks%20union%20members%20join%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild%20-%20American%20Federation%20of%20Television%20and%20Radio%20Artists%20(SAG-AFTRA)%20and%20Writers%20Guild%20of%20America%20(WGA)%20union%20members%20on%20the%20picket%20line.%3Cp%3EKatie%20McTiernan%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Image%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20national%20labor%20agency%20says%20it%20processed%20over%202%2C500%20petitions%20to%20form%20a%20new%20union%20in%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20up%20from%20fewer%20than%201%2C700%20petitions%20in%20the%202021%20fiscal%20year%2C%20an%20increase%20of%2058%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20agency%20also%20saw%20a%2010%25%20uptick%20in%20allegations%20of%20employer%20%26quot%3Bunfair%20labor%20practices%26quot%3B%20in%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20a%20new%20liberal%20majority%20at%20the%20federal%20agency%20that%20rules%20on%20employer-worker%20disputes%20has%20coincided%20with%20a%20boon%20in%20collective%20organizing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Labor%20Relations%20Board%20announced%20Friday%20that%20petitions%20to%20form%20unions%20continue%20to%20rise%20following%20a%20%26quot%3Bdramatic%20surge%26quot%3B%20the%20year%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fiscal%20year%202023%2C%20which%20ended%20September%2030%2C%20the%20NLRB%20said%20there%20were%202%2C594%20union%20representation%20petitions%20filed%20with%20its%20regional%20field%20offices%2C%20an%20uptick%20of%203%25%20from%20the%20year%20before.%20Compared%20to%20fiscal%20year%202021%2C%20when%20Biden%20entered%20office%2C%20requests%20for%20union%20recognition%20are%20up%20