sinessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Finsider-today%5C%22%3EInsider's%20daily%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20altered%20many%20aspects%20of%20jobs%20as%20well%20as%20careers.%20And%20the%20changes%20in%20networking%20closely%20mirror%20how%20workplace%20trends%20have%20evolved%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20probably%20better%20than%2050%25%20back%20to%20normal%2C%20but%20probably%20not%20as%20much%20as%2075%25%20back%20to%20normal%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20Fletcher%2C%20cofounder%20of%20executive%20search%20firm%20Intersection%20Growth%20Partners%2C%20told%20me%20about%20the%20volume%20of%20networking%20he's%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20line%20of%20work%20depends%20on%20networking%2C%20and%20he's%20noticed%20a%20decline%20in%20touch%20points%20across%20the%20board%2C%20including%20conference%20attendance%20and%20one-on-one%20meetups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20experts%20told%20me%20the%20way%20we%20network%20has%20changed%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%20and%20discussed%20the%20modifications%20they've%20witnessed%20and%20experienced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20media%20%3D%20networking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22562%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22social%20media%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6387f6d7c989f000184c1dfa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22421%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EUdemy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Campanaro%2C%20an%20area%20director%20at%20staffing%20firm%20Adecco%2C%20told%20me%20people%20are%20finding%20commonality%20in%20a%20virtual%20world%2C%20which%20can%20then%20pivot%20into%20an%20in-person%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20pinging%20people%20on%20LinkedIn.%20We're%20getting%20friend%20requests%20on%20Facebook%2C%20engaging%20in%20tweets%2C%20liking%20pictures%20on%20Instagram%2C%20viewing%20videos%20on%20TikTok%20%E2%80%94%