ate%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20ensure%20that%20freshly%20elected%20assemblies%20are%20in%20place%20in%20any%20state%20in%20which%20assemblies%20have%20either%20been%20dissolved%20or%20have%20run%20out%20their%20due%20term.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20this%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20Commission%20seeks%20reports%20from%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20on%20security%20details%2C%20and%20on%20obtaining%20necessary%20law%20and%20order%20infrastructure%20to%20operationalise%20elections%20in%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20manner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPresumably%2C%20the%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20remark%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20not%20yet%20conducive%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20must%20have%20been%20based%20on%20a%20report%20from%20the%20home%20ministry%2C%20one%20that%20has%20not%20been%20made%20public.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%2C%20even%20though%20no%20day%20passes%20when%20we%20are%20not%20told%20how%20all%20things%20big%20and%20small%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdilution-of-article-370-brought-unprecedented-progress-and-security-to-jk-centre-tells-sc%5C%22%3Eincluding%20the%20security%20situation%2C%20in%20the%20UT%20has%20seen%20a%20mind-blowing%20transformation%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20better.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBetter%2C%20that%20is%2C%20for%20all%20purposes%20other%20than%20for%20holding%20elections%20to%20the%20local%20bodies%2C%20panchayats%2C%20and%20a%20prospective%20state%20assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20elections%20to%20the%20state%20assembly%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20have%20been%20held%20successfully%20in%20times%20truly%20dire%2C%20for%20example%20in%201996.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20sit-in%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20the%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20announcements%20on%20October%209%2C%20the%20next%20day%20saw%20a%20sit-in%20by%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20regional%20political%20parties%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20in%20the%20Maharaja%20Park%20in%20Jammu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20speaker%20had%20pretty%20much%20the%20same%20flummoxed%20poser%3A%20if%20the%20government%20claims%20things%20have%20improved%20by%20leaps%20and%20bounds%2C%20why%20no%20elections%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnsurprisingly%2C%20the%20impartiality%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20come%20into%20question%2C%20given%20that%20elections%20in%20Ladakh%20were%20held%20without%20incident%2C%20although%20China%2C%20the%20baleful%20ogre%2C%20sits%20right%20over%20the%20head%20in%20that%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInevitably%2C%20observations%20were%20made%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20shying%20away%20from%20a%20certain%20drubbing%2C%20as%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERiddle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20we%20comprehend%20the%20yes-no%20riddle%20with%20respect%20to%20elections%20to%20a%20prospective%20assembly%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHelp%20here%20comes%20from%20something%20the%20honourable%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20Manoj%20Sinha%2C%20said%20some%20time%20ago.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20asked%20a%20media%20house%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20poll%20among%20the%20people%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20that%20poll%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkoWmbpY_WjQ%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20the%20honourable%20LG%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2080%25%20Kashmiris%20responded%20that%20they%20would%20vote%20for%20the%20same%20central%20rule%20that%20now%20obtains%20in%20the%20UT.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%2C%20as%20Hamlet%20would%20say%2C%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpalpable%20hit