0against%20it%3F%20Not%20that%20it%20has%20done%20anything%20substantial%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20but%20even%20strategically%20it%20was%20idiotic%20to%20push%20oneself%20in%20a%20corner%20and%20lose%20all%20sympathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14145007%2FF8Uka5bWcAEcrIw.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14145007%2FF8Uka5bWcAEcrIw.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14145007%2FF8Uka5bWcAEcrIw-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14145007%2FF8Uka5bWcAEcrIw-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680094%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETrial%20of%20destruction%20in%20Gaza%20after%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20offensive%20following%20Hamas%20rocket%20attacks.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40UNRWA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20act%20of%20Hamas%20is%20indefensible.%20It%20was%20a%20callous%20and%20irresponsible%20act%20of%20violence%20that%20would%20in%20the%20long%20run%20achieve%20little%20and%20which%20was%20bound%20to%20cause%20misery%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20who%20have%20longer%20memories%20question%20the%20sincerity%20of%20the%20expression%20of%20revulsion%20by%20the%20international%20community%20after%20the%20Hams%20attack.%20The%20world%20has%20been%20watching%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20personnel%20arresting%20and%20killing%20the%20Gaza%20people%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20Without%20any%20provocation.%20The%20world%20knows%20well%20that%20the%20government%20of%20Israel%20is%20aiding%20and%20supporting%20t