uals.%20So%2C%20this%20individuality%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20sacrificed%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20collective%20cause%2C%20however%20great%20it%20might%20sound.%20Nothing%20is%20more%20sacred%20than%20the%20life%20of%20an%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20the%20last%20seven%20days%2C%20we%20can%20say%20that%20Hamas%20violated%20this%20basic%20principle.%20But%20the%20larger%20and%20much%20longer%20context%20of%20the%20last%20decades%20of%20continuous%20violation%20of%20it%20by%20Israel%20cannot%20be%20put%20aside.%20Without%20the%20Israeli%20terror%2C%20the%20terror%20of%20Hamas%20would%20not%20have%20existed.%20If%20the%20world%20wants%20Hamas%20to%20be%20irrelevant%2C%20it%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20first%20discipline%20its%20pampered%20Israel%20which%20has%20been%20acting%20like%20a%20bully%20for%20the%20last%20seven%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697275302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14143541%2FF8QQypiXAAAyXOe.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwithout-israels-oppression-of-palestinians-hamas-terrorism-would-have-never-existed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20Hamas%20has%20done%20is%20inexcusable%2C%20but%20a%20pertinent%20question%20for%20the%20civilised%20world%20is%20whether%20it%20will%20ever%20condemn%20Israel%20for%20daily%20humiliation%20of%20Palestinians%20for%20seven%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwithout-israels-oppression-of-palestinians-hamas-terrorism-would-have-never-existed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20forgets%20to%20wear%20correct%20jersey%20vs%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697275084000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104421004%2Cimgsize-58536.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimeso