ent%2C%3Cem%3E%20The%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modis-inauguration-hint-in-ayodhya-call-to-vips%2Fcid%2F1973216%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20could%20offer%20inaugural%20prayers%20there%20between%2011%20am%20and%20noon%20on%20that%20day.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20decided%20at%20a%20meeting%20two%20days%20ago%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20would%20offer%20the%20first%20prayer%20at%20the%20new%20Ram%20temple%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20PMO%20(Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office)%20has%20agreed%20to%20it%20but%20it%20would%20be%20unwise%20on%20our%20part%20to%20announce%20the%20chief%20guest%E2%80%99s%20programme.%20The%20PMO%20will%20announce%20it%20soon%20if%20everything%20goes%20well.%20The%20temple%20will%20be%20opened%20for%20the%20general%20public%20on%20January%2026%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20daily%20quoted%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Shree%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20had%20issued%20its%20appeal%20to%20VIPs%20without%20citing%20any%20reason.%E2%80%9DChief%20ministers%2C%20governors%2C%20ambassadors%20and%20all%20those%20who%20enjoy%20visit-and-security-related%20protocol%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%20We%20or%20the%20local%20administration%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20welcome%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20trust%2C%20told%20reporters%20at%20his%20office%20in%20the%20temple%20town%20on%20Friday%2C%20October%2013.%20However%2C%20he%20had%20sidestepped%20questions%20if%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%20was%20being%20planned%20on%20the%20said%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%20devotees%20abroad%20planning%20to%20offer%20prayers%20at%20the%20temple%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20foreign%20department%20of%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20where%20h