warns-12984255%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-uk-could-be-complicit-in-gaza-war-crimes-tory-mp-warns-12984255%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%3A%20Taxmen%20Raid%20Contractor%20Behind%20'40%25%20Commission'%20Charge%20Against%20BJP%2C%20Seize%20Rs%2042%20Crore%20Cash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14123008%2FThe-Wire-41.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIncome%20tax%20officials%20seized%20Rs%2042%20crore%20in%20cash%20from%20the%20residence%20of%20the%20son%20of%20a%20Bengaluru%20civil%20contractor%20who%20has%20links%20to%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20contractor%20in%20question%2C%20R.%20Ambikapathy%2C%20was%20vocal%20in%20accusing%20the%20previous%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20of%20extorting%2040%25%20commission%20from%20civil%20contractors%20%E2%80%93which%20figured%20prominently%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20elections%20that%20unseated%20the%20BJP%20from%20power%20in%20the%20state.%20Ambikapathy%20is%20the%20vice-president%20of%20Bruhat%20Bengaluru%20Mahanagara%20Palike%20(BBMP)%20Contractors%E2%80%99%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIT%20officials%20have%20been%20carrying%20out%20a%20series%20of%20raids%20over%20the%20last%20two%20days%20at%20properties%20linked%20to%20contractors%20who%20carry%20out%20civil%20construction%20works%20for%20BBMP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20seized%20cash%20is%20part%20of%20the%20commission%20that%20is%20to%20be%20paid%20to%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20by%20contractors%20in%20exchange%20for%20authorities%20releasing%20Rs%20650%20crore%20for%20the%20works%20done%20by%20contractors%20in%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20along%20with%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20in%20neighbouring%20state%20of%20Telangana%2C%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20seized%20cash%20was%20to%20fund%20the%20Congress%20election%20campaign%20in%20Telangana.%20Telangana%20is%20going%20to%20polls%20on%20November%2030%2C%20and%20Congress%20is%20a%20serious%20contender%20for%20power%20against%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fit-raids-bengaluru-civil-contractors-bjp-congresss-funds-telangana-polls-8981942%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BJP%20MLC%20and%20spokesperson%20N.%20Ravikumar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Rs%2042%20crore%20found%20with%20a%20contractor%20is%20the%20commission%20for%20the%20release%20of%20Rs%20650%20crore%20of%20payments%20to%20contractors.%20Karnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20deputy%20CM%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20should%20take%20moral%20responsibility%20and%20quit.%20There%20should%20be%20a%20detailed%20probe%20into%20the%20funds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20leader%20H.D.%20Kumaraswamy%20echoed%20the%20views%20of%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cash%20was%20found%20following%20the%20release%20of%20Rs%20650%20crore%20of%20payments%20to%20a%20few%20contractors.%20It%20seems%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20money%20is%20illegal.%20Who%20are%20the%20people%20behind%20this%20and%20what%20is%20the%20percentage%20of%20kickbacks%3F%E2%80%9D%20Kumaraswamy%20said%20on%20social%20media%20Friday.%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20party%20is%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20information%20is%20that%20the%20carton%20boxes%20with%20the%20money%20were%20to%20be%20transported%20to%20Telangana%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20also%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmbikapathy%20from%20whom%20the%20money%20was%20seized%20is%20the%20husband%20of%20Ashwathamma%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20the%20Congress%20councillor%20from%20the%20RT%20Nagar%20region%20in%20the%20city.%20Ashwathamma%20also%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20sister%20of%20Akhanda%20Srinivasamurthy%2C%20who%20was%20denied%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20in%20the%20recent%20Assembly%20polls%20after%20he%20had%20a%20bad%20falling%20out%20with%20D.%20K.%20Shivakumar%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%20this%20year%2C%20Shivakumar%20had%20threatened%20to%20withhold%20the%20payments%20to%20contractors%20for%20works%20done%20during%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government.%20He%20had%20said%20his%20government%20would%20not%20pay%20anyone%20who%20would%20present%20bills%20without%20showing%20proof%20of%20actual%20work%20on%20the%20ground.%20According%20to%20contractors%2C%20payments%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20710%20crore%20from%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government%20are%20pending%20to%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20contractors%20had%20also%20sought%20the%20intervention%20of%20the%20governor%20while%20accusing%20Shivakaumr%20of%20demanding%20bribes%20for%20the%20release%20of%20payments.%20They%20had%20said%20he%20must%20swear%20if%20he%20is%20not%20demanding%20bribes.%20However%2C%20the%20contractors%20later%20withdrew%20their%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20has%20been%20accusing%20Shivakumar%20of%20%E2%80%9CDKS%20tax%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20release%20of%20payments%20to%20contractors%20who%20had%20carried%20out%20works%20under%20the%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20IT%20raids%2C%20Shivakumar%20said%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cpolitically%20motivated%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20IT%20department%20would%20not%20take%20any%20action%20without%20a%20political%20motive.%20We%20know%20everything%20that%20is%20happening.%20It%20is%20being%20done%20in%20states%20where%20the%20Opposition%20is%20ruling%3B%20it%20is%20being%20done%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20specifically%20about%20the%20link%20between%20the%20release%20of%20payments%20and%20the%20unaccounted%20money%20seized%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20know.%20I%20do%20not%20need%20to%20respond%20to%20people%20who%20speak%20on%20the%20streets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20about%20the%20BJP%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697266949000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14123008%2FThe-Wire-41.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengaluru-rs-42-crore-cash-seized-from-congress-linked-contractor-bjp-brs-see-telangana-poll-link%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IT%20officials%20seized%20cash%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2042%20crore%20from%20a%20property%20linked%20to%20R.%20Ambikapathy%2C%20who%20was%20vocal%20in%20accusing%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government%20of%20extorting%2040%25%20commission%20from%20contractors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengaluru-rs-42-crore-cash-seized-from-congress-linked-contractor-bjp-brs-see-telangana-poll-link%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Varun%20Dhawan%20sports%20Team%20India%20jersey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697266898000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104417825%2Cimgsize-109609.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Findvspak-world-cup-varun-dhawan-sports-team-india-jersey-says-khelenge-hum-shaan-se-see-pic-inside%2Farticleshow%2F104417903.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104417903.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20musical%20ceremony%20is%20scheduled%20just%20before%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20high-voltage%20match%20at%20the%20Narendra%2